N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 13 ยง 300.5 - Filing date

State Regulations

On the day the administrator receives the prescribed filing fee, the administrator
shall date-stamp the request for arbitration form. Such date shall be considered the filing date. Notes
